---
title: Chicken Fajita Bowls with Spiced Rice
description: Everything you love about fajitas piled into a bowl! Spiced rice, Mexican-seasoned chicken thighs, chunky salsa, tangy lime crema and cheese. Mix, match and dig in!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bols-style-fajitas-au-poulet-13dab244.jpg
